00:30:23,428 --> 00:30:26,158
Take the St. Charles
line to Napoleon.

397
00:30:32,170 --> 00:30:33,762
Hey! Hey!

398
00:30:54,092 --> 00:30:57,584
Where in God's name have you been?
Get in here.

