Tizzy whispering.

478
00:35:48,953 --> 00:35:53,117
They said I was gonna die
soon, but maybe not.

479
00:35:55,360 --> 00:35:56,884
You're odd.

480
00:35:57,662 --> 00:36:00,529
You're different than
anybody I've ever met.

481
00:36:03,701 --> 00:36:05,862
- May I?
- Okay.

482
00:36:13,111 --> 00:36:15,545
